{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000227", "chronotag": "1739874519426", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL227", "numeroOrdreDepot": "227", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0134", "triAmendement": "jcaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaacx", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA722150", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO840056", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA643175", "PA607395", "PA720362", "PA642695", "PA793210"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Houli&#233;,  Mme&#160;Dupont, M.&#160;Travert, M.&#160;Belhaddad, M.&#160;Bothorel et M.&#160;Panifous"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 14", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 14", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 14", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0134.asp#D_Article_14"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Par l&#x2019;article 14, les auteurs de la proposition de loi ont entendu sanctionner par une amende l&#x2019;abandon ou le d&#x00E9;p&#x00F4;t intentionnel ou par imprudence, inattention ou n&#x00E9;gligence d&#x2019;objets dans les emprises ou les v&#x00E9;hicules affect&#x00E9;s au transport public de marchandises ou de voyageur.</p><p>Le caract&#x00E8;re intentionnel ou non d&#x2019;une telle infraction est quasi-impossible &#x00E0; &#x00E9;tablir. <br>&nbsp;<br>En outre, la cr&#x00E9;ation d&#x2019;un nouveau d&#x00E9;lit comme la perspective d&#x2019;une amende n&#x2019;auront aucun effet contre l&#x2019;&#x00E9;tourderie ou la distraction des propri&#x00E9;taires ou des voyageurs.</p><p>Enfin, il convient de rappeler aux auteurs de la proposition de loi que l&#x2019;abandon intentionnel fait d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; l&#x2019;objet d&#x2019;une incrimination au titre de l&#x2019;article 2242-4 du code des transports de sorte que cet article est superf&#x00E9;tatoire.</p><p>Il doit donc &#x00EA;tre supprim&#x00E9;.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-23", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-27T17:20:41+01:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000227?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "74350", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}